      "side": 1,
      "message": "\u003e The testcase has an example ((debug) log message).\n\nI meant a real example in a repository that would potentially use this.  I did see the test case.  I really don\u0027t understand where this fits in the middle between \"Use PDI\" and \"Use strings\".  This seems like a medium that\u0027s worse than either of those two and we\u0027d probably direct people to use one or the other in that case.\n\n\u003e Maybe someone will find a creative use for them\n\nWould like to see some of these creative uses before we deem this to be a good idea.  sdbusplus is a limited API on purpose.",
      "parentUuid": "e6a43c43_18cb23a1",
